  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and smoked paprika, cooking for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the arborio rice and toast it lightly, stirring constantly for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk, saffron infusion, and broth, bringing the mixture to a gentle boil.",
    "Add the chopped almonds to the pan, ensuring they mingle with the rice.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and let the paella simmer for 15 minutes or until the liquid is absorbed.",
    "Remove from heat, fluff the rice with a fork, garnish with parsley, and serve with lemon wedges."
